{
  "stem": "1502.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was one of the largest textile dealers in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Hitler made him president.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They also included the chief rabbi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they promised these people that they will be protected if they work with them and if they do what they tell them to do.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I would say that, in my opinion, that some Jewish people that were in that Judenrat were anxious to be there because they saw in this a way of saving their lives and the lives of their families.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Even so, I would give them the credit that they did not know, at that time, that they're going to kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They thought there'll be restrictions of Jews that they will help enforce.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I, I think had they known what that really means and what will come out of that committee, I don't think that these people would have joined the committee.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But in any case, they made-- whatever they did, they made the task of the Gestapo easier because they worked with them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The main thing what they did was to supply the Gestapo with all the names and addresses of the Jews in the city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were very clever, the Germans, how to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were working with a plan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They worked scientifically, psychologically.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They didn't want the Jews to know what was going to happen to them because they wanted the minimum of resistance.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Also, they did want to keep the image.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This was Western Europe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It wasn't Poland, and not everybody was an anti-Semite.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They wanted to keep the image that they're not murderers in Western Europe.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
